Florence Giorgetti https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Florence_Giorgetti 0 Florence Giorgetti (born 15 February 1944) is a French stage and film actress. She was nominated for the César Award for Best Supporting Actress for her role in La Dentellière. Florence_Giorgetti ( born 15_February_1944 ) is a_French_stage_and_film_actress .
